=============================================================================

Deployment via Systemd (Alternative to Docker)

=============================================================================

1. Place this file in /etc/systemd/system/gatekeeper.service

2. Update the User, Group, and WorkingDirectory paths

3. Run: sudo systemctl daemon-reload

4. Run: sudo systemctl enable --now gatekeeper

=============================================================================

[Unit]
Description=NetSuite Requirement Gatekeeper (Slack Bot)
After=network.target

[Service]

Ensure the bot runs under a non-root user

User=ubuntu
Group=ubuntu

Update to where you cloned the repo

WorkingDirectory=/opt/ns_slack_bot_v3

Use the virtual environment's python

ExecStart=/opt/ns_slack_bot_v3/venv/bin/python app.py

Automatically restart if the app crashes

Restart=always
RestartSec=5

Keep logs unbuffered

Environment=PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target